name: The devil Maze ver. pre alpha 0.1
name_original: The devil Maze ver. pre alpha 0.1
description:
The devil Maze ver. pre alpha 0.1 is a platformer game developed by SoldamChef. It was originally released in 2017.
You can play The devil Maze ver. pre alpha 0.1 on PC and macOS. The game is sold via itch.io.
